dcterms:description: eICU is sampled from the eICU Collaborative Research Database, a multi-center database with anonymised hospital patient records. eICU is publicly available after registration, including completion of a training course in research with human subjects and signing of a responsible data use agreement.
dcterms:title: eICU

dcterms:description: MIMIC-III is an extensive, freely-available database of over 40,000 critical care patients. To complement MIMIC experiments with heterogeneous feature types and data dimensionality, different datasets were extracted for the experiment.
dcterms:title: MIMIC-III
